@startuml
title Final Project - Communication and Notifications Diagram

left to right direction
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 70
hide methods
hide circle

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam PackageBorderColor #334155
skinparam PackageBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam ClassBorderColor #334155
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor white

package "5) Communication & Notifications" {
    class User {
        +id
        +name
        +email
        +requested_role
    }

    class Message {
        +id
        +subject
        +body
        +read_at
    }

    class Notification {
        +id
        +type
        +read_at
    }

    class Review {
        +id
        +student_name
        +rating_score
        +uploaded_at
    }

    class TeacherResource {
        +id
        +category
        +name
        +download_count
    }

    class CourseClass {
        +id
        +capacity
        +teacher_id
    }
}

User "1" <-- "0..*" Message : sends
User "1" <-- "0..*" Message : receives
User "1" <-- "0..*" Notification : receives
User "1" <-- "0..*" Review : writes
User "1" <-- "0..*" TeacherResource : uploads
CourseClass "1" <-- "0..*" TeacherResource : shared with class

User -[hidden]-> Message
Message -[hidden]-> Notification
Notification -[hidden]-> Review
Review -[hidden]-> TeacherResource
TeacherResource -[hidden]-> CourseClass

note bottom of Notification
Notifications are used for approvals, new messages,
attendance events, resource actions, and announcements.
end note

@enduml
